source="MessageBody"><a title="https://eszu.sk/akreditovane-studijne-programy/asp-foazos/fyzioterapia-mgr-ef/" href="https://eszu.sk/akreditovane-studijne-programy/asp-foazos/fyzioterapia-mgr-ef/#1759154398240-4-101759154511096" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-auth="NotApplicable" data-linkindex="15">MAGISTERSKÉ ŠTÚDIUM EXTERNÁ FORMA</a></li></ul></div></div><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 32px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-4"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><b>Rádiologická technika</b></span></p><ul><li><a title="https://eszu.sk/akreditovane-studijne-programy/asp-foazos/radiologicka-technika-bc-df/" href="https://eszu.sk/akreditovane-studijne-programy/asp-foazos/radiologicka-technika-bc-df/#1759154398240-4-101759154511096" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-auth="NotApplicable" data-linkindex="17"><span data-olk-copy-source="MessageBody">BAKALÁRSKE ŠTÚDIUM DENNÁ FORMA</span></a></li></ul></div></div><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 32px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div></div></div></div><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-4"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element  vc_custom_1775569785602" ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><b>Urgentná zdravotná starostlivosť</b></span></p><ul><li><a title="https://eszu.sk/akreditovane-studijne-programy/asp-foazos/urgentna-zdravotna-starostlivost-bc-df/" href="https://eszu.sk/akreditovane-studijne-programy/asp-foazos/urgentna-zdravotna-starostlivost-bc-df/#1759154398240-4-101759154511096" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-auth="NotApplicable" data-linkindex="19">BAKALÁRSKE ŠTÚDIUM DENNÁ FORMA</a></li><li><a title="https://eszu.sk/akreditovane-studijne-programy/asp-foazos/urgentna-zdravotna-starostlivost-bc-ef/" href="https://eszu.sk/akreditovane-studijne-programy/asp-foazos/urgentna-zdravotna-starostlivost-bc-ef/#1759154398240-4-101759154511096" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-auth="NotApplicable" data-linkindex="21">BAKALÁRSKE ŠTÚDIUM EXTERNÁ FORMA</a></li></ul></div></div><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 32px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div></div></div></div><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-4"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element  vc_custom_1775569857863" ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><b>Fyziologická a klinická výživa</b></span></p><ul><li><a title="https://eszu.sk/akreditovane-studijne-programy/asp-foazos/fyziologicka-a-klinicka-vyziva-bc-ef/" href="https://eszu.sk/akreditovane-studijne-programy/asp-foazos/fyziologicka-a-klinicka-vyziva-bc-ef/#1759154398240-4-101759154511096" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-auth="NotApplicable" data-linkindex="23"><span data-olk-copy-source="MessageBody">BAKALÁRSKE ŠTÚDIUM EXTERNÁ FORMA</span></a></li></ul></div></div><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 32px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-4"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><b>Dentálna hygiena</b></span></p><ul><li><a title="https://eszu.sk/akreditovane-studijne-programy/asp-foazos/dentalna-hygiena-bc-ef/" href="https://eszu.sk/akreditovane-studijne-programy/asp-foazos/dentalna-hygiena-bc-ef/#1759154398240-4-101759154511096" target="_blank" rel="