apper"><h3 style="text-align: center;font-family:Abril Fatface;font-weight:400;font-style:normal" class="vc_custom_heading vc_do_custom_heading" >Odborová komisia doktorandského štúdia FVZ</h3><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 32px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-8"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><p style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Členovia Odborovej komisie doktorandského štúdia FVZ:</strong></p><ul><li style="font-weight: 400;">prof. PhDr. Róbert Babeľa, PhD., MBA, MSc. (HTA), FISAC</li><li style="font-weight: 400;">prof. MUDr. Mária Belovičová, PhD.</li><li style="font-weight: 400;">prof. Ing. Nadežda Jankelová, PhD., MPH</li><li style="font-weight: 400;">doc. MUDr. Štefánia Moricová, PhD., MPH</li><li style="font-weight: 400;">PhDr. Juraj Tihányi, PhD., MPH, univerzitný docent</li></ul></div></div><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 32px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div></div></div></div><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-4"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="standard-arrow list-divider bullet-top"><p><strong>Zápisnice:</strong></p><ul><li><a href="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/Zapisnica-zo-zasadnutia-12.10.2023.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Zápisnica zo zasadnutia 12.10.2023</a></li><li><a href="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/Zapisnica-per-rollam-4.4.2024-7.4.2024.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Zápisnica per rollam 4.4.2024-7.4.2024</a></li><li><a href="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/Zapisnica-per-rollam-15.4.2024-17.4.2024.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Zápisnica per rollam 15.4.2024-17.4.2024</a></li><li><a href="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/Zapisnica-per-rollam-25.6.2024-28.6.2024.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Zápisnica per rollam 25.6.2024-28.6.2024</a></li><li><a href="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/Prerokovanie-informacie-o-obhajobach.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Prerokovanie informácie o obhajobách</a></li><li><a href="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/Prerokovanie-rocneho-hodnotenia-doktorandov-za-akademicky-rok-2023-1.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Prerokovanie ročného hodnotenia doktorandov za akademický rok 2023</a></li><li><a href="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/Prerokovanie-studijnych-a-1.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Zápisnica z prerokovania a schválenia študijných a vedeckých (výskumných) plánov novoprijatých doktorandov</a></li><li><div class="page" title="Page 1"><div class="layoutArea"><div class="column"><div class="page" title="Page 1"><div class="layoutArea"><div class="column"><p><a href="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/Evidencia-vysledkov-prijimacie-konania-na-doktorandske-studium-na-akademicky-rok-2024-1.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Evidencia výsledkov prijímacie konania na doktorandské štúdium na akademický rok 2024/2025</a></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></li></ul></div><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 32px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>
