data-popmake="{&quot;id&quot;:25115,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;anketa-vas-nazor-nas-zaujima&quot;,&quot;theme_id&quot;:14468,&quot;cookies&quot;:[],&quot;triggers&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;click_open&quot;,&quot;settings&quot;:{&quot;extra_selectors&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;cookie_name&quot;:null}}],&quot;mobile_disabled&quot;:null,&quot;tablet_disabled&quot;:null,&quot;meta&quot;:{&quot;display&quot;:{&quot;stackable&quot;:false,&quot;overlay_disabled&quot;:false,&quot;scrollable_content&quot;:false,&quot;disable_reposition&quot;:false,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;medium&quot;,&quot;responsive_min_width&quot;:&quot;0%&quot;,&quot;responsive_min_width_unit&quot;:false,&quot;responsive_max_width&quot;:&quot;100%&quot;,&quot;responsive_max_width_unit&quot;:false,&quot;custom_width&quot;:&quot;640px&quot;,&quot;custom_width_unit&quot;:false,&quot;custom_height&quot;:&quot;380px&quot;,&quot;custom_height_unit&quot;:false,&quot;custom_height_auto&quot;:false,&quot;location&quot;:&quot;center&quot;,&quot;position_from_trigger&quot;:false,&quot;position_top&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;position_left&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;position_bottom&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;position_right&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;position_fixed&quot;:false,&quot;animation_type&quot;:&quot;fade&quot;,&quot;animation_speed&quot;:&quot;350&quot;,&quot;animation_origin&quot;:&quot;center top&quot;,&quot;overlay_zindex&quot;:false,&quot;zindex&quot;:&quot;1999999999&quot;},&quot;close&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;button_delay&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;overlay_click&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;esc_press&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;f4_press&quot;:false},&quot;click_open&quot;:[]}}"><div id="popmake-25115" class="pum-container popmake theme-14468 pum-responsive pum-responsive-medium responsive size-medium"><div class="pum-content popmake-content" tabindex="0"><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><p class="elementToProof"><b>Váš názor nás zaujíma</b></p><p class="elementToProof">Milí študenti SZU, Centrum pre podporu vnútorného systému kvality v spolupráci s IT oddelením spustilo anketu v MAIS s cieľom získavania relevantnej spätnej väzby od študentov. V ankete študenti majú možnosť hodnotiť kvalitu výučby a učiteľov, praktickú výučbu/klinickú prax/stáž, študijný program a prostredie a podporných služieb fakulty/univerzity.</p><p class="elementToProof"><strong>Anketa je sprístupnená od 25.04.2024 do 30.06.2024.</strong> Anketa je prístupná v <a href="https://mstudent.szu.sk/student" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MAIS, rozhranie ŠTUDENT</a> v záložke ANKETA. Prihlásiť sa do MAIS je potrebné cez webový prehliadač, NIE cez mobilnú aplikáciu. Anketa je anonymná. Výsledky ankety budú slúžiť ako východisko pre návrh a prijímanie opatrení na zlepšovanie kvality štúdia. Výsledky ankety, reakcie a pripomienky budú zverejnené na webovom sídle SZU v doméne fakulty.</p><p>Ďakujeme za Váš čas a ochotu vyplniť anketu.</p></div></div><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 32px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><p><b>Your opinion matters</b></p><p class="elementToProof">Dear students SMU, The Support Centre of the Internal Quality System in cooperation with IT department have launched a survey in MAIS with the aim of obtaining relevant feedback from students. In the survey, students can evaluate the quality of teaching and teachers, practical training/clinical practice/internship, the study programme, the environment, and support services of the faculty/university.</p><p class="elementToProof"><strong>The survey is available from 25/04/2024 till 30/06/2024.</strong> The survey is accessible in MAIS, the <a href="https://mstudent.szu.sk/student" target="_blank" rel="noopener">STUDENT interface</a>, and the SURVEY tab. It is necessary to log in to MAIS through a web browser, NOT through a mobile application. The survey is anonymous. The results of the survey will serve as a starting point for the design and adoption of measures to improve the quality of study. The results of the survey, reactions and comments will be published on the SMU website in the faculty domain.</p><p>Thank you for your time and willingness to fill out the survey.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>
<button type="button" class="pum-close popmake-close" aria-label="Close">
×			</button></div></div><div
