n-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: center;"><b>Tlačivá, dokumenty, legislatíva</b></p></div></div><div class="hr-thin style-line" style="width: 80%;border-color: #dd3333;border-top-width: 2px;"></div><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 32px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><div class="vc_tta-container" data-vc-action="collapse"><div class="vc_general vc_tta vc_tta-tabs vc_tta-color-blue vc_tta-style-classic vc_tta-shape-square vc_tta-spacing-1 vc_tta-o-no-fill vc_tta-tabs-position-left vc_tta-controls-align-left "><div class="vc_tta-tabs-container"><ul class="vc_tta-tabs-list" role="tablist"><li class="vc_tta-tab" data-vc-tab role="presentation"><a href="#1699878298835-631a2b2e-c3b916998790865191699879442055" data-vc-tabs data-vc-container=".vc_tta" role="tab" aria-selected="false" id="tab-1699878298835-631a2b2e-c3b916998790865191699879442055"><span class="vc_tta-title-text">Doplňujúce pedagogické štúdium - tlačivá</span></a></li><li class="vc_tta-tab" data-vc-tab role="presentation"><a href="#1699878298846-d119481c-68a516998790865191699879442055" data-vc-tabs data-vc-container=".vc_tta" role="tab" aria-selected="false" id="tab-1699878298846-d119481c-68a516998790865191699879442055"><span class="vc_tta-title-text">Atestácie- tlačivá</span></a></li><li class="vc_tta-tab" data-vc-tab role="presentation"><a href="#1699878362608-20d542ce-6f7f16998790865191699879442055" data-vc-tabs data-vc-container=".vc_tta" role="tab" aria-selected="false" id="tab-1699878362608-20d542ce-6f7f16998790865191699879442055"><span class="vc_tta-title-text">Dokumenty</span></a></li><li class="vc_tta-tab" data-vc-tab role="presentation"><a href="#1699878376560-9c4a40e4-762e16998790865191699879442055" data-vc-tabs data-vc-container=".vc_tta" role="tab" aria-selected="false" id="tab-1699878376560-9c4a40e4-762e16998790865191699879442055"><span class="vc_tta-title-text">Legislatíva</span></a></li></ul></div><div class="vc_tta-panels-container"><div class="vc_tta-panels"><div class="vc_tta-panel" id="1699878298835-631a2b2e-c3b916998790865191699879442055" data-vc-content=".vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="vc_tta-panel-heading"><h4 class="vc_tta-panel-title"><a href="#1699878298835-631a2b2e-c3b916998790865191699879442055" data-vc-accordion data-vc-container=".vc_tta-container"><span class="vc_tta-title-text">Doplňujúce pedagogické štúdium - tlačivá</span></a></h4></div><div class="vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Doplňujúce pedagogické štúdium &#8211; tlačivá</strong></p></div></div><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 25px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><div class="standard-arrow list-divider bullet-top"><ul><li>Žiadosť o zaradenie [<a href="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Ziadost_o_zaradenie_do_DPS.docx" target="_blank" rel="noopener">DOCx</a>][<a href="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Ziadost_o_zaradenie_do_DPS.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PDF</a>]</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="vc_tta-panel" id="1699878298846-d119481c-68a516998790865191699879442055" data-vc-content=".vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="vc_tta-panel-heading"><h4 class="vc_tta-panel-title"><a href="#1699878298846-d119481c-68a516998790865191699879442055" data-vc-accordion data-vc-container=".vc_tta-container"><span class="vc_tta-title-text">Atestácie- tlačivá</span></a></h4></div><div class="vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><p style="text-align: center;"><strong>ATESTÁCIE </strong><strong>&#8211; tlačivá</strong></p></div></div><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 25px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><div class="standard-arrow list-divider bullet-top"><ul><li>Žiadosť o vykonanie atestácie [<a href="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Ziadost_o_vykonanie_atestacie.doc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">DOC</a>][<a href="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Ziadost_o_vykonanie_atestacie.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PDF</a>]</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="vc_tta-panel" id="1699878362608-20d542ce-6f7f16998790865191699879442055" data-vc-content=".vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="vc_tta-panel-heading"><h4 class="vc_tta-panel-title"><a href="#1699878362608-20d542ce-6f7f16998790865191699879442055" data-vc-accordion data-vc-container=".vc_tta-container"><span class="vc_tta-title-text">Dokumenty</span></a></h4></div><div class="vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><p style="text-align: center;"><strong>DOKUMENTY</strong></p></div></div><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 25px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><div class="standard-arrow list-divider bullet-top"><ul><li><a href="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/Dokumenty/szu/smernice/Smernica-c-5-2019-o-nalezitostiach-zaverecnych-prac.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Smernica náležitostiach záverečných prác</a></li><li><a href="https://eszu.sk/smernice/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Smernica o školnom a poplatkoch</a></li><li><a href="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Studijny_-poriadok_DPS_FOaZOS.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Študijný poriadok pre DPŠ</a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="vc_tta-panel" id="1699878376560-9c4a40e4-762e16998790865191699879442055" data-vc-content=".vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="vc_tta-panel-heading"><h4 class="vc_tta-panel-title"><a href="#1699878376560-9c4a40e4-762e16998790865191699879442055" data-vc-accordion data-vc-container=".vc_tta-container"><span class="vc_tta-title-text">Legislatíva</span></a></h4></div><div class="vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><p style="text-align: center;"><strong>LEGISLATÍVA</strong></p></div></div><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 25px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><div class="standard-arrow list-divider bullet-top"><ul><li><a title="https://www.slov-lex.sk/pravne-predpisy/SK/ZZ/2019/138/20230901.html" href="https://www.slov-lex.sk/pravne-predpisy/SK/ZZ/2019/138/20230901.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">zákon o pedagogických zamestnancoch a odborných zamestnancoch</a></li><li><a title="https://www.slov-lex.sk/pravne-predpisy/SK/ZZ/2019/361/" href="https://www.slov-lex.sk/pravne-predpisy/SK/ZZ/2019/361/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">vyhláška MŠVVaŠ č. 361/2019 o vzdelávaní v profesijnom rozvoji</a></li><li><a title="https://www.minedu.sk/data/att/12056.zip" href="https://www.minedu.sk/data/att/12056.zip" target="_blank" rel="noopener">pokyn ministra č. 39/2017 – profesijné štandardy</a> pre jednotlivé kategórie a podkategórie pedagogických zamestnancov a odborných zamestnancov škôl a školských zariadení</li><li><a title="https://www.minedu.sk/profesijny-rozvoj-pedagogickych-zamestnancov-a-odbornych-zamestnancov/" href="https://www.minedu.sk/profesijny-rozvoj-pedagogickych-zamestnancov-a-odbornych-zamestnancov/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">metodické usmernenia ministra</a> – profesijný rozvoj pedagogických zamestnancov a odborných zamestnancov</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>
