rapper"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><h4 style="text-align: center;">Aktivity katedry LABORATÓRNYCH VYŠETROVACÍCH METÓD V ZDRAVOTNÍCTVE</h4></div></div><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 32px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-3"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div  class="wpb_single_image wpb_content_element vc_align_left"><figure class="wpb_wrapper vc_figure">
<a href="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/studetska-kvapka-krvi_uvodny-obrazok--768x1024.jpg" target="_blank" data-large_image_width="1536" data-large_image_height="2048"  class="vc_single_image-wrapper   vc_box_border_grey rollover"   ><img data-lazyloaded="1" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIyMjUiIGhlaWdodD0iMzAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMjI1IDMwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgc3R5bGU9ImZpbGw6I2NmZDRkYjtmaWxsLW9wYWNpdHk6IDAuMTsiLz48L3N2Zz4=" width="225" height="300" data-src="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/studetska-kvapka-krvi_uvodny-obrazok--225x300.jpg" class="vc_single_image-img attachment-medium" alt="" title="študetská kvapka krvi_úvodný obrázok" decoding="async" data-srcset="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/studetska-kvapka-krvi_uvodny-obrazok--225x300.jpg 225w, https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/studetska-kvapka-krvi_uvodny-obrazok--768x1024.jpg 768w, https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/studetska-kvapka-krvi_uvodny-obrazok--300x400.jpg 300w, https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/studetska-kvapka-krvi_uvodny-obrazok--1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/studetska-kvapka-krvi_uvodny-obrazok--280x373.jpg 280w, https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/studetska-kvapka-krvi_uvodny-obrazok-.jpg 1536w" data-sizes="(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px"  data-dt-location="https://eszu.sk/studetska-kvapka-krvi_uvodny-obrazok/" /></a></figure></div><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 32px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div></div></div></div><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-9"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div><ul><li class="xmsonormal"><h3>Študentská kvapka krvi</h3></li></ul></div><div><p class="xmsonormal">Dňa 24. októbra 2023 sa na Fakulte zdravotníctva SZU v spolupráci s Národnou transfúznou službou SR a katedrou laboratórnych vyšetrovacích metód v zdravotníctve zrealizoval <b><i>odber študentskej kvapky krvi</i></b><i>.</i> Darovať krv prišlo 50 študentov v zastúpení všetkých študijných programov fakulty. Veľmi si ceníme takú vysokú účasť i keď nie všetci študenti spĺňali prísne kritériá darcovstva.</p></div><div><p class="xmsonormal">Ďakujeme všetkým dobrovoľným darcom krvi za darovanie život zachraňujúcej tekutiny. Uvedenú aktivitu zároveň vnímame aj ako príležitosť k zvyšovaniu povedomia o potrebe pravidelného darovania krvi a krvných derivátov na zabezpečenie lepšej dostupnosti pre pacientov v núdzi.</p></div></div></div><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 32px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid vc_column-gap-10 vc_row-o-content-middle vc_row-flex"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-2"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div  class="wpb_single_image wpb_content_element vc_align_center"><figure class="wpb_wrapper vc_figure">
<a href="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/studetska-kvapka-krvi-1-768x1024.jpg" target="_blank" data-large_image_width="1536" data-large_image_height="2048"  class="vc_single_image-wrapper   vc_box_border_grey rollover"   ><img data-lazyloaded="1" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxNTAiIGhlaWdodD0iMTUwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMTUwIDE1MCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgc3R5bGU9ImZpbGw6I2NmZDRkYjtmaWxsLW9wYWNpdHk6IDAuMTsiLz48L3N2Zz4=" width="150" height="150" data-src="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/studetska-kvapka-krvi-1-150x150.jpg" class="vc_single_image-img attachment-thumbnail" alt="" title="študetská kvapka krvi 1." decoding="async" data-srcset="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/studetska-kvapka-krvi-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/studetska-kvapka-krvi-1-300x300.jpg 300w" data-sizes="(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px"  data-dt-location="https://eszu.sk/studetska-kvapka-krvi-1/" /></a></figure></div><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 10px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div></div></div></div><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-2"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div  class="wpb_single_image wpb_content_element vc_align_center"><figure class="wpb_wrapper vc_figure">
<a href="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/studetska-kvapka-krvi-2-768x1024.jpg" target="_blank" data-large_image_width="1536" data-large_image_height="2048"  class="vc_single_image-wrapper   vc_box_border_grey rollover"   ><img data-lazyloaded="1" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxNTAiIGhlaWdodD0iMTUwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMTUwIDE1MCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgc3R5bGU9ImZpbGw6I2NmZDRkYjtmaWxsLW9wYWNpdHk6IDAuMTsiLz48L3N2Zz4=" width="150" height="150" data-src="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/studetska-kvapka-krvi-2-150x150.jpg" class="vc_single_image-img attachment-thumbnail" alt="" title="študetská kvapka krvi 2." decoding="async" data-srcset="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/studetska-kvapka-krvi-2-150x150.jpg 150w, https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/studetska-kvapka-krvi-2-300x300.jpg 300w" data-sizes="(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px"  data-dt-location="https://eszu.sk/studetska-kvapka-krvi-2/" /></a></figure></div><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 10px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div></div></div></div><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-2"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div  class="wpb_single_image wpb_content_element vc_align_center"><figure class="wpb_wrapper vc_figure">
