er"><div class="dt-fancy-separator h4-size" style="width: 100%;"><div class="dt-fancy-title" style="color: #2e3192;"><span class="separator-holder separator-left" style="border-color: #81d742;"></span>Programová rada pre HIK na SZU<span class="separator-holder separator-right" style="border-color: #81d742;"></span></div></div><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 32px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-8"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="standard-arrow bullet-top"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element "><div class="wpb_wrapper"><p><strong>Zloženie Programovej rady pre habilitačné a inauguračné konania</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><em>predseda: </em></p><ul><li>doc. MUDr. Štefánia Moricová, PhD., MPH</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p><em>členovia: </em></p><ul><li>prof. PhDr. Zuzana Slezáková, PhD., MPH</li><li>prof. MUDr. Zuzana Krištúfková, PhD., MPH</li><li>prof. MUDr. Daniel Pinďák, PhD.</li><li>doc. MUDr. Miroslav Žigrai, PhD.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 20px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div></div></div></div><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-4 vc_col-has-fill"><div class="vc_column-inner vc_custom_1677827240904"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="standard-number-list list-divider bullet-top"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element "><div class="wpb_wrapper"><p><strong>Zápisnice:</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p></div></div><div class="standard-number-list bullet-top"><ul><li><a href="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/Zapisnica-z-porady_PR-HIK-SZU_06.04.2022.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Zapisnica z porady_PR HIK SZU_06.04.2022</a></li><li><a href="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/Zapisnica-z-porady_PR-HIK-SZU_04.04.2022.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Zapisnica z porady_PR HIK SZU_04.04.2022</a></li><li><a href="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/Zapisnica-z-porady_PR-HIK-SZU_24.01.2022.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Zapisnica z porady_PR HIK SZU_24.01.2022</a></li></ul></div></div><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 20px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-8"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="standard-arrow bullet-top"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element "><div class="wpb_wrapper"><p><strong>Vyjadrenia k plneniu kritérií na získanie vedecko-pedagogických titulov</strong></p><ul><li><a href="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/Zapis-o-vyjadreni-k-plneniu_Bakos.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Zápis o vyjadrení k plneniu &#8211; MUDr. Marian Bakoš, PhD., MPH</a></li><li><a href="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/Zapis-o-vyjadreni-k-plneniu_Bernadic.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Zápis o vyjadrení k plneniu &#8211; MUDr. Michal Bernadič, PhD., MPH</a></li><li><a href="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/Zapis-o-vyjadreni-k-plneniu_Skladany.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Zápis o vyjadrení k plneniu &#8211; MUDr. Ľubomír Skladaný, PhD.</a></li><li><a href="https://eszu.sk/wp-content/uploads/Zapis-o-vyjadreni-k-plneniu_Vohnout.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Zápis o vyjadrení k plneniu &#8211; MUDr. Branislav Vohnout, PhD.</a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 20px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div></div></div></div><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-4 vc_col-has-fill"><div class="vc_column-inner vc_custom_1677827240904"><div class="wpb_wrapper"></div></div></div></div></p></div>
