Budova: L12, 2. poschodie</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 10px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><p>Organizovanie pracovného programu a pracovných stretnutí kvestora, preberanie informácií pre kvestora, kompetencia presadzovať požiadavky kvestora voči zamestnancom SZU.</p></div></div><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 10px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><div class="vc_separator wpb_content_element vc_separator_align_center vc_sep_width_100 vc_sep_border_width_2 vc_sep_pos_align_center vc_separator_no_text vc_sep_color_grey wpb_content_element  wpb_content_element" ><span class="vc_sep_holder vc_sep_holder_l"><span class="vc_sep_line"></span></span><span class="vc_sep_holder vc_sep_holder_r"><span class="vc_sep_line"></span></span></div><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 10px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 32px"><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element  vc_custom_1682506808770" ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><h5 style="text-align: left;">Mgr. Daniel Ďurfina<br />
